      "text": [
        "3629 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"كَفَى بِالْمَرْءِ إِثْماً أَنْ يُضَيِّعَ مَنْ يَعُولُ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3629 - Imam (as) said: \"It is sufficient for a man to be sinful if he neglects those he is responsible for.\""
        ]
      }
